text: lung cancer is the number one cancer
killer worldwide claiming more lives
than breast colon and croste cancer
combined the root cause of why it's such
a deadly disease is that we don't catch
it soon enough because our current
screening test a CT scan is not cost
effective for the vast majority of
patients working together our team has
come up with an elegant solution the L
card the L card is a simp gas sensor
that detects molecules unique to the
exhale breath of lung cancer patients
and sends a diagnosis to a smartphone
you breathe on this and it tells a
smartphone whether you have lung cancer
it's cheaper than CT scans it's easier
to use and it's more accurate all told
this is a market opportunity north of 8
to9 billion
